\c 7
\s Ukuhlakanipha kuhle okwedlula konke
\p
\v 1 Ibizo \add elihle\x + Zaga 22.1.\x*\add* lingcono kulamafutha amahle; losuku lokufa kulosuku lokuzalwa kwakhe\x + 12.7.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Kungcono ukuya endlini yokulila kulokuya endlini yedili; ngoba lokhu kuyisiphetho sakhe wonke umuntu; lophilayo uzakubeka enhliziyweni yakhe\x + 7.21. Neh. 2.12. Hlab. 90.12.\x*.
\v 3 Usizi lungcono kulohleko\x + 1.18. 2.23. 11.10. Zaga 17.25. Zaga 14.13.\x*, ngoba ngokudana kobuso\x + 2 Kor. 7.10.\x* inhliziyo yenziwa ngcono\x + Hlu. 18.20. Hlu. 19.6.\x*.
\v 4 Inhliziyo yabahlakaniphileyo isendlini yokulila, kodwa inhliziyo yezithutha isendlini yentokozo.
\v 5 Kungcono ukuzwa ukukhuza kohlakaniphileyo kulokuthi umuntu ezwe ingoma yezithutha\x + Hlab. 141.5. Zaga 13.18. 15.31,32.\x*.
\v 6 Ngoba njengokuchachamba kwameva ngaphansi kwembiza\x + Hlab. 58.9. 118.12.\x* lunjalo uhleko lwesithutha. Lokhu lakho kuyize\x + 2.2.\x*.
\v 7 Isibili ucindezelo\x + 4.1.\x* lwenza ohlakaniphileyo abe luhlanya\x + Jobe 12.17.\x*, lesipho siyayichitha inhliziyo\x + Eks. 23.8. Zaga 17.23.\x*.
\v 8 Singcono isiphetho sento kulokuqala kwayo\x + Mat. 10.22.\x*; kungcono ukubekezela komoya kulokuziphakamisa komoya\x + Zaga 14.29. Jobe 6.11.\x*.
\v 9 Ungaphangisi emoyeni wakho\x + 5.2. 8.3.\x* ukuthukuthela\x + Zaga 14.29. Jobe 6.11.\x*, ngoba ukuthukuthela kuhlala esifubeni sezithutha\x + Zaga 14.33.\x*.
\v 10 Ungatsho \add ukuthi\add*: Kwenziwa yini ukuthi insuku zakuqala zibe ngcono kulalezi? Ngoba kawubuzi ngenhlakanipho ngalokhu.
\p
\v 11 Inhlakanipho yinhle ilelifa, njalo kulenzuzo\x + 2.15.\x* kwabalibonayo ilanga\x + 11.7.\x*.
\v 12 Ngoba inhlakanipho iyisivikelo, imali iyisivikelo; kodwa ubungcono bolwazi \add yikuthi\x + 1.3.\x*\add* lunika impilo\x + Zaga 3.18.\x* kubaninilo\x + 5.11.\x*.
\v 13 Nakana umsebenzi kaNkulunkulu; ngoba ngubani olakho ukwelula\x + 1.15. 12.9. Dan. 4.36.\x* akugobisileyo\x + 1.15. 12.9. Dan. 4.36.\x*\x + Hlab. 146.9. Jobe 19.6.\x*?
\p
\v 14 Thokoza ngosuku lokuphumelela, kodwa ngosuku lobubi nakana\x + Dute. 28.47.\x*: UNkulunkulu ulwenzile lalolu lwaba njengalolo, ukuze umuntu angatholi lutho oluzakuba khona emva kwakhe\x + 3.18.\x*.
\v 15 Konke ngikubonile ensukwini zokuyize kwami: Kukhona olungileyo obhubhela ekulungeni kwakhe\x + 8.14.\x*, njalo kukhona omubi owelula \add impilo yakhe\add* ebubini bakhe\x + 8.12,13. Jobe 6.11.\x*.
\v 16 Ungabi ngolungileyo ngokudlulisayo, futhi ungahlakaniphi okwedlulisileyo; uzichithelani\x + 2.15.\x*?
\v 17 Ungabi ngomubi ngokudlulisayo, futhi ungabi yisiwula; uzafelani kungakabi yisikhathi sakho\x + Zaga 10.27.\x*?
\v 18 Kuhle ukuthi ubambelele kulokhu\x + 7.16.\x*, yebo\x + 7.17.\x*, ungabuyisi isandla sakho lakulokho; ngoba omesabayo uNkulunkulu uzaphepha kukho konke\x + 11.6.\x*.
\v 19 Inhlakanipho iyamqinisa ohlakaniphileyo\x + 9.16,18. Zaga 21.22. 24.5. Zaga 8.14.\x* okwedlula ababusi abalitshumi abasemzini\x + 8.8. 10.5. Gen. 42.6.\x*.
\v 20 Ngoba kakulamuntu olungileyo emhlabeni owenza okuhle\x + 7.28. 1 Kho. 8.46. 2 Lan. 6.36. Zaga 20.9.\x* angoni\x + 7.28. 1 Kho. 8.46. 2 Lan. 6.36. Zaga 20.9.\x*.
\v 21 Futhi ungabeki inhliziyo yakho emazwini wonke akhulunywayo\x + Gal. 6.1.\x*, ukuze ungezwa ukuthi inceku yakho iyakuthuka\x + Zaga 30.10.\x*.
\v 22 Ngoba ngezikhathi ezinengi lenhliziyo yakho iyakwazi ukuthi lawe uqobo ubathukile abanye\x + Gal. 6.1.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Konke lokhu ngikuhlolile ngenhlakanipho, ngathi: Ngizahlakanipha; kodwa kwakukhatshana lami\x + Roma 1.22.\x*.
\v 24 Okukhatshana, lokujule kakhulu\x + Roma 11.33.\x*, ngubani ozakufumana\x + Jobe 28.12,20.\x*?
\v 25 Ngaphenduka mina lenhliziyo yami ukwazi lokuhlola lokudinga inhlakanipho\x + 1.17.\x*, lesizatho \add sezinto\add*, lokwazi inkohlakalo yobuwula, lobuthutha bobuhlanya\x + 7.27. 9.10. 7.29. 2.12.\x*.
\v 26 Ngasengithola okubaba kulokufa\x + Zaga 5.4.\x*: Owesifazana onhliziyo yakhe iyimijibila lamambule, \add le\add*zandla zakhe ziyizibopho\x + Zaga 12.12. Zaga 23.28.\x*. Olungileyo phambi kukaNkulunkulu uzaphepha kuye, kodwa isoni sizabanjwa nguye\x + Zaga 22.14.\x*.
\v 27 Khangela, yilokhu engikutholileyo, utsho umTshumayeli\x + 1.1.\x*, \add ngibeka\add* okunye kokunye, ukuthola isizatho \add sezinto\add*,
\v 28 umphefumulo wami osasidinga kodwa kangisitholanga. Indoda eyodwa phakathi kwenkulungwane ngayithola\x + 7.20.\x*\x + Jobe 33.23.\x*, kodwa owesifazana phakathi kwabo bonke labo kangimtholanga\x + 7.25. 1 Kho. 11.3.\x*.
\v 29 Khangela, yilokhu kuphela engikutholileyo, ukuthi uNkulunkulu wamenza umuntu waqonda\x + Gen. 1.27.\x*; kodwa bona sebedinge\x + Gen. 3.6,7.\x* amacebo amanengi\x + 2Chr 26.15.\x*.
